#: ../../source/unit/dac2.rst:2 ea205fb8918e4ae396c0b4e7475a86ea
msgid "DAC2 Unit"
msgstr "DAC2 Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/dac2.rst:7 2d407500f70b4478b266435e4960237c
msgid ""
"The `Dac2` class interfaces with a GP8413 15-bit Digital to Analog "
"Converter (DAC), capable of converting digital signals into two channels "
"of analog voltage output, ranging from 0-5V and 0-10V."
msgstr ""
"`Dac2` 类用于与 GP8413 15 位 Digital to Analog Converter (DAC) "
"交互，可将数字信号转换为两路模拟电压输出，输出范围为 0-5V 和 0-10V。"

